						<div class="postbody">Been seeing a few posts on this and have been experimenting with a few things.  I'm trying to get a good handle on the best method for sub pixel movement (seems imperative to implement, lest everything always move by multiples of 'one pixel').  Things like acceleration are impossible without this.  Just wondering if anyone has a good method?<br /><br />Thanks!</div>

